Class GUIWorld

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • GUIWorld

  • public class GUIWorld
extends javafx.application.Application
    Handles the display of all controls for the simulation Each control has an associated event handler which utilises specific button/menu commands Interacts with the SimWorld by calling constructors on a SimWorld Object
    See Also:
    functions in source for relationship between action and button calls
